âœ… Use case: Conditional sensitive handling

7. regex() â€“ Match string patterns
hcl
Copy
Edit
regex("[0-9]+", "ec2-1234") # matches "1234"
âœ… Use case: Validating or extracting IDs

ğŸ“˜ Real-World Use: Combining Functions
hcl
Copy
Edit
output "subnet_cidrs" {
  value = [for i in range(3) : cidrsubnet("10.0.0.0/16", 8, i)]
}
âœ… Output: 3 unique /24 subnets â€” automated and elegant!

